Detailed Description

EntityInfo is a data structure for storing the information about an entity loaded in by EntityManager from an XML file.

EntityInfo objects are created internally by the EntityManager, I don't think there is a need to give anyone else access to them. Entity contain the string name to refer to this entity by. The XML filename this entity's definition is contained in. It also contains a pointer to the factory that can create this type of entity. This is determined by the type.
